title: The Worm Ouroboros
creator: E. R. Eddison
description: LibriVox recording of The Worm Ouroboros by E R Eddison. Read by Jason Mills. This classic 1922 fantasy novel brings you to a strange and lovely world where a young lord wrestles King Gorice for his land's freedom, where unscalable mountains can only be conquered by stubbornness and hippogriffs, where the great explorer Lord Gro finds himself continually driven to betrayal, where sweet young women occasionally fall for evil wizards, and where the heroes actually win their hearts' desire.
